<HL>
   Aerovox to Reduce Odd Lots
</HL>
<DATE>
05/16/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C19
</SO>
<CO>
   ARVX
</CO>
<IN>
STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK)
</IN>
<LP>
   NEW BEDFORD, Mass. -- Aerovox Inc. said stockholders who
own fewer than 100 shares are being offered a program under
which they can sell their odd-lot shares -- without cost.
   The maker of capacitors said the offer is available to
holders of record May 2 and will expire June 22.
</LP>
